physical_examinations.relevant_findings: Fetal morphological study revealed several brain and physical abnormalities including absent cavum septum pellucidum, prefrontal area midline findings, hypoplastic cerebellum, presence of nasal bone, flattened frontal area with prefrontal edema, subjective micrognathia, mild bilateral ocular proptosis, normal cardiac study with slight levocardia, normal male genitalia, fixed wrist joint, feet in hyperflexion with little mobility.
